videos.headline: Thorson's TD gives Northwestern early lead
videos.description: Clayton Thorson takes it in from 4 yards out to put Northwestern ahead of Iowa 7-0.

videos.headline: Wadley's TD evens score with Northwestern
videos.description: Iowa RB Akrum Wadley runs it in from 5 yards out to tie the game at 7 with Northwestern.

videos.headline: Northwestern ties game on great diving grab

videos.headline: Thorson and Carr connect for second time
videos.description: Clayton Thorson hits Austin Carr for the second time in the game to extend Northwestern's lead over Iowa to 38-24.
